{"tid":2236831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得其實自己根本唔配有依家嘅生活？","createTime":"2020-10-09T18:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T19:17:17.000Z","uid":371862,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f89097bb7d2a5dcf73af522ba1a0aaf54429dbd","tid":2236831,"uid":371862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:35:22.000Z","msg":"當有班手足每日都擔心緊自己嘅前途<br />\n面對緊官司 可能下一次審完就要還押<br />\n又可能因為場運動失去咗好多嘢<br />\n<br />\n但係我竟然每日返學放學 同朋友吹下水<br />\n嘻嘻哈哈咁又過一日 <br />\n想做啲嘢去幫佢哋 但係又會有好重嘅無力感<br />\n望下自己 再望下佢哋 <br />\n就會覺得好對佢哋唔住 <br />\n點解自己仲可以過住正常生活<br />\n<br />\n有時都好想做返隻港豬<br />\n咩都唔諗  但係真係好難 我做唔到<br />\n<br />\n嗰種自責同無力感有冇人明<br />\n由其係依家街頭抗爭嘅低潮<br />\n好對唔住嗰班付出咗咁多嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n唉 我都唔知自己講緊啲乜 有冇人明<br />\n怪自己進化得太遲 係街頭上嘅付出唔多<br />\n怪自己嘅懦弱 <br />\n<br />\n一諗到呢啲嘢個人就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5334005310db1ca8f534b08acc480f478b3297","tid":2236831,"uid":371862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:37:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以入嚟同我傾幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f46be41e14a0f12c45546a44f8b9d041f5caf46","tid":2236831,"uid":186800,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"奉勸一句 淺淺地黃好啦 深黃真係on9 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea1032c7b4c9dea9ffd0aa8e49df27d4cd77fcc","tid":2236831,"uid":371862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:43:50.000Z","msg":"開咩台先有人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006917d2e01461232b39383357fe8baf3abb98b4","tid":2236831,"uid":371862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f46be41e14a0f12c45546a44f8b9d041f5caf46","tid":2236831,"uid":186800,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"奉勸一句 淺淺地黃好啦 深黃真係on9 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10